# Naming & Coding Style

## File names

- Lowercase only; multi-word with `-`: `student-flag-history.ts`, `chat-api.ts`
- **Avoid** capitals in filenames: not `ChatApp.ts`, `TryHard.ts`

## Variables & types

- **camelCase** — variables, functions, methods
- **PascalCase** — classes, interfaces, types
- **UPPER_SNAKE** — constants (optional)

## Style

- OOP where domain concepts fit; singletons for `EngEAI_MongoDB`, `RAGApp`, etc.
- **Backend types:** `src/types/shared.ts`
- **Frontend types:** `public/scripts/types.ts` — no imports from `src/`; keep in sync with shared.ts manually
- Debug logs: `// DEBUG:` or `// TEMP:` — remove before done

## Build

- Frontend source: `public/scripts/` → `public/dist/`
- HTML scripts: `/dist/*.js` only, never `/scripts/*.ts`
